  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460650/extras/f9c0ee9a07bf307cc10dc761d66db362.webp?t=1692668249\" width=616 height=24 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460650/extras/4d2ed1694373d30b0d0bf14066b30395.poster.avif?t=1692668249\" width=616 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460650/extras/4d2ed1694373d30b0d0bf14066b30395.webm?t=1692668249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460650/extras/4d2ed1694373d30b0d0bf14066b30395.mp4?t=1692668249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Lodestar is a puzzle adventure crafting game that you can play alone but is better with up to 8 friends.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460650/extras/9fa5c6c4ecd4c04d136839fdf160b971.webp?t=1692668249\" width=616 height=24 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460650/extras/a167c7a4350d218d1efec8c07827de46.poster.avif?t=1692668249\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460650/extras/a167c7a4350d218d1efec8c07827de46.webm?t=1692668249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460650/extras/a167c7a4350d218d1efec8c07827de46.mp4?t=1692668249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Solve puzzles as you explore each new area, and use all tools available to get past several challenging environments.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460650/extras/fbf8559930670006415ef3476486f0cf.webp?t=1692668249\" width=616 height=24 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460650/extras/81a722d49f2c07fa574f824968f8cf7d.poster.avif?t=1692668249\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460650/extras/81a722d49f2c07fa574f824968f8cf7d.webm?t=1692668249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460650/extras/81a722d49f2c07fa574f824968f8cf7d.mp4?t=1692668249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Lost in space, work with your friends to survive and be the first of mankind to communicate with an intelligent species - solving the puzzle of what happened to the previous crew along the way.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460650/extras/3f3f8e48ee976b1bab6408fc063e30bc.webp?t=1692668249\" width=616 height=24 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460650/extras/2cc854378fbbbca35f80d6887ba98014.poster.avif?t=1692668249\" width=616 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460650/extras/2cc854378fbbbca35f80d6887ba98014.webm?t=1692668249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460650/extras/2cc854378fbbbca35f80d6887ba98014.mp4?t=1692668249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Survive by gathering resources to improve yourself through new abilities and upgrades.  You'll need these to help you navigate the hostile planets!<br><br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Multiplayer campaign with online co-op!<br></li><li> Zelda-like puzzles that must be solved with various abilities!<br></li><li> Craft new resources to purchase hundreds of upgrades.<br></li><li> Explore a series of handcrafted planets that get you coming back for new secrets!<br></li><li> Survive a variety of life-threatening monsters and bosses!</li></ul>",
